<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Property Offer Accepted</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .property-details, .offer-details {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Congratulations, Your Offer Has Been Accepted!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
      <p>We are excited to inform you that your offer for the property at {{propertyAddress}} has been accepted!</p>
      <div class="offer-details">
        <h3>Offer Details:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Offer Price:</strong> ${{offerPrice}}</li>
          <li><strong>Status:</strong> Accepted</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      {{!-- <p>Next steps:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Contact your real estate agent to finalize the paperwork.</li>
        <li>Schedule a home inspection.</li>
        <li>Review and sign the purchase agreement.</li>
      </ol> --}}

      <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please do not hesitate to contact us.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
